<h2>Your offer was declined</h2>

<p>Hi <%= @buyer.display_name %>,</p>

<p>Unfortunately, your offer for the <strong><%= @listing.brand_name %></strong> gift card was declined by the seller.</p>

<div class="card-details">
  <h3><%= @listing.brand_name %> Gift Card</h3>
  <div class="detail-row">
    <span class="detail-label">Card Value:</span>
    <span class="detail-value"><%= number_to_currency(@listing.balance) %></span>
  </div>
  <% if @transaction.sale? %>
    <div class="detail-row">
      <span class="detail-label">Your Offer:</span>
      <span class="detail-value"><%= number_to_currency(@transaction.amount) %></span>
    </div>
  <% else %>
    <div class="detail-row">
      <span class="detail-label">Offered Card:</span>
      <span class="detail-value"><%= @transaction.offered_gift_card.brand_name %> (<%= number_to_currency(@transaction.offered_gift_card.balance) %>)</span>
    </div>
  <% end %>
</div>

<p>Don't worry! There are plenty of other great deals on Cardly. Browse the marketplace to find more gift cards.</p>

<p style="text-align: center;">
  <%= link_to "Browse Marketplace", marketplace_url, class: "btn" %>
</p>
